            "show_description": false,
            "show_read_more": true,
            "default_open": false,
            "heading": "Details",
            "heading_font_size": "body-small",
            "text": "<p>Crafted with thoughtful design and timeless appeal, this piece features a flattering silhouette made to move with you. From the soft drape of the fabric to the subtle finishing touches, every element is designed to feel as beautiful as it looks. Whether worn casually or dressed up, it’s a staple you’ll return to again and again.</p>",
