            "show_read_more": true,
            "default_open": false,
            "heading": "Shipping & Returns",
            "heading_font_size": "body-small",
            "text": "<p>We offer fast, reliable shipping and easy returns on all unworn items within our return window. Once your order ships, you’ll receive a tracking link so you can follow it every step of the way. If you need a different size or style, exchanges are simple — just visit our Returns page or contact our team for assistance.</p>",
